<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_21d1ae89-1aff-4db1-8482-860226d709a9" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>B4D2</sptc><title id="_cfabf5be-f62d-4e9f-85f5-cb6900e80dbc">General requirements</title><archive-num>2019: B4.2</archive-num><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/7389_0.7.0.xml" variation="VIC" variation-type="REPLACE">VIC REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_92b1d291-b26f-4f5e-812b-232e062c9c67" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_15aa105f-a718-4156-89ad-253af340a133">SubClause</title><num/><p>Fire-fighting water services for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2522_1.14.0.xml#_36cc6151-3825-4649-9b75-c6f04ad0ff01" id="_47a3a686-ddc5-44ce-8587-2746dd90a2cd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">Class 2 to Class 9</xref> buildings and structures must comply with the requirements of <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/30#_3c0138fa-b0ae-47d1-894d-b3c4672352eb" id="_3957f2d5-ad2d-446a-ae27-39be5b1c9bb8" publishing-id="vol1" scope="external" type="part">Part E1</xref> of Volume One of the NCC.</p></subclause><callout id="_8d6fc1c2-f495-4a6c-b96e-cb3b1f70f9cc"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>NCC Volume One requires the installation of fire-fighting equipment including fire hose reels, fire hydrants and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1199_0.7.0.xml#_ac370c9b-7389-4daa-ac5b-338e11dc43e7" id="_72645e48-a2fb-49e1-a6d1-a7f4388f79d3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">automatic</xref> fire suppression systems in certain types of buildings.</p><p>The installation of fire-fighting water services in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2526_1.8.0.xml#_aaefaaca-c6f4-4f31-b202-f2866a59e6ac" id="_1c8ed82c-731c-4d45-a9e0-43f7fd0702a9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">Class 1</xref> buildings is not required by NCC Volume Two, however, where these services are installed voluntarily, they must be in accordance with Part B4.</p></callout></clause>